He only got few years.
Did he say eight?

619
01:39:53,280 --> 01:39:55,681
Was that it? - I'm sorry.

620
01:39:56,040 --> 01:40:00,602
Was that all? Is that
the best you can do?

621
01:40:02,040 --> 01:40:04,407
He murdered my wife!

622
