623
01:40:20,360 --> 01:40:23,284
The termination
of your employment, -

624
01:40:23,480 --> 01:40:26,962
who was the initiator?
- The employer.

625
01:40:30,480 --> 01:40:32,847
The house is your own?
- Yes.

626
01:40:33,240 --> 01:40:35,527
Well, 50% belongs to the bank.

627
01:40:35,960 --> 01:40:38,930
We don't do
loan repayments.

628
