726
01:53:13,960 --> 01:53:16,281
Besides it's real.

727
01:53:19,400 --> 01:53:21,926
I'm doing okay.

728
01:53:23,000 --> 01:53:25,810
This is a start.

729
01:53:26,360 --> 01:53:29,091
A new beginning.

730
01:53:29,280 --> 01:53:32,727
To everything.
- If you say so.

731
01:54:36,960 --> 01:54:38,962
Mommy?

732
